snippet.title: Mortal Kombat 1: Khaos Reigns Official Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
His Era of Peace was never meant to last. This September, Khaos Reigns.

Khaos Reigns releases September 24. https://www.mortalkombat.com/purchase

It's In Our Blood. Discover a reborn Mortal Kombat Universe created by Fire God Liu Kang. Mortal Kombat 1 ushers in a New Era of the iconic franchise with a new fighting system, game modes, and Fatalities!
